eu.amidst.dynamic.datastream

Interface DynamicDataInstance

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Assignment, DataInstance, DynamicAssignment

    public interface DynamicDataInstance
extends DataInstance, DynamicAssignment
    The DynamicDataInstance interface represents a dynamic data sample. It extends the DataInstance and DynamicAssignment interfaces. Hence, it can be also interpreted as a dynamic assignment to a set of Variable objects.

    An example of use of the DynamicDataInstance interface can be found in eu.amidst.dynamic.examples.datastream
